## How To
# append this to your i3 config file
## keyboard layout
# bind Alt+Shift to execute set_keyboard.sh
bindcode mod1+50 exec --no-startup-id exec /bin/bash -c "$HOME/.config/i3/set_keyboard.sh signal"
# execute "set_keyboard.sh us", which sets the keyboard layout to us
exec --no-startup-id /bin/bash "$HOME/.config/i3/set_keyboard.sh signal us"
